title: The Cure Trilogy - Bloodflowers 2000.avi
description:
"Bloodflowers" portion of Trilogy DVD. This was part of a larger torrent called "The greatest Cure collection that will ever be available", but the audio and video for the Bloodflowers segment were out of sync.

To fix the problem, the Bloodflowers section was resynched with VirtualDub, video/audio otherwise untouched.
